Version 0.1.3

 * Support CC, CFLAGS, LDFLAGS override in Makefile
 * Support DESTDIR in Makefile install targets
 * Install manual pages into share/man/man1 directory
 * Prioritize MDM_LIB over $PATH in mdm.screen


